description: Object type, has influence on the value of concession_code_csx  in dev_datavault.datavault.sat_cos_vehicle_last_previous_placement. Available values: KFZ =Kraftfahrzeig (lorry), FAWEG=Fahrweg (road), SBFZ=Strassenbahnfahrzeug (train, tram), HAGEB=building
Location code consisting of at least 4 capitals, the three first ones indicating the town and the last one being the first letter of the address
Name of the location, e.g. Delft; Schieweg
Blocking Code U=Record is not visible W=Warning for being used
Employee code of the person who has edited the record, e.g. ESIKKEMA
Reference, Four digit code for vehicles, or another alphanumeric values for other objects.
X coordinate, It tells how far to the left or right point lies along the X-axis (Longitude)/GPS Coordinates(Co-ordinates in RD)
Y coordinate, It tells how far to the left or right point lies along the Y-axis (Latitude)/GPS Coordinates(Co-ordinates in RD)
Z coordinate, Z coordinate if applicable for floors.
Foreign key to the WSAD table. Is empty.
Client number, foreign key to the WKST table.
Internal address number, contact person, foreign key to the WADR table.
